## What this section is about

This section collects company news and practical materials that help foundry shops keep their processes stable and predictable.

Here you will find:

- news about Intema Group and our operations;
- updates to the product line and formulations;
- case studies from foundry implementations;
- overview articles on casting technologies and mould/core processes.

## What you can find here

- **Product release notes.** Short descriptions, areas of use, key benefits.
- **Changes in formulations and documentation.** What has been updated, how it may affect your process, where to download the latest TDS and MSDS files.
- **Practical notes and recommendations.** Short articles with tips on process tuning, scrap reduction, and introducing new materials.
- **Case studies.** Real stories of how our solutions support foundry operations.

## Stay up to date

We regularly add new items to this section. Check back to stay up to date with product changes and to find ideas for improving your foundry processes.
